            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="text-center py-16 bg-white rounded-2xl container-shadow mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                Launch Your Income Stream for <span class="text-blue-600">Free</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Discover the best zero-cost tools and strategies to build a profitable digital business. Your profit starts at $1, not $1 minus hosting fees.
            </p>
            <a href="#tools" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-full shadow-lg text-white bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                Explore the Free Toolkit →
            </a>
        </section>

        <!-- New Strategy Guide Section -->
        <section id="strategy-guide" class="py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl container-shadow mb-12 border-t-4 border-blue-500">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">The Two Pillars of Zero-Cost Income</h3>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 text-center">This entire website model is built on two proven, low-maintenance strategies that require zero upfront cash investment.</p>

                <div class="space-y-10">

                    <!-- Pillar 1: Affiliate Marketing -->
                    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-3 flex items-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101M16.969 14.121l-2.828 2.829m-6.364-6.364l2.828-2.828a4 4 0 015.656 0l4 4a4 4 0 010 5.656l-1.102 1.101"></path></svg>
                            Pillar 1: Affiliate Marketing (The Easiest Start)
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">
                            **Affiliate marketing** is where you earn a commission by recommending products or services (like the tools listed below) to your audience. When a user clicks your unique affiliate link and makes a qualifying action (like a purchase or a paid sign-up), you get paid. Since the programs are free to join and you're promoting existing products, your cost is **zero**.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="mt-4 text-gray-600 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>**Your Role:** Create valuable, helpful content (like guides or reviews) that naturally includes the affiliate links.</li>
                            <li>**Zero Cost:** You never buy inventory, handle customer service, or pay for storage.</li>
                            <li>**Income Potential:** Commissions typically range from 5% to 50% depending on the product, leading to substantial passive revenue.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pillar 2: Passive Ad Revenue -->
                    <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3 flex items-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19V6l12-3v14L9 19z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 5v14"></path></svg>
                            Pillar 2: Passive Ad Revenue (Scale for Recurring Income)
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">
                            Once your free website starts getting consistent **traffic** (visitors), you can enroll in passive display ad networks like **Google AdSense**. These networks automatically place relevant advertisements on your pages. You earn money based on impressions (CPM) or clicks (CPC).
                        </p>
                        <ul class="mt-4 text-gray-600 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                            <li>**Setup:** Easy integration with a small code snippet provided by the ad network.</li>
                            <li>**Passive:** Revenue is generated automatically without new content or direct selling.</li>
                            <li>**Requirement:** Focus on high-quality content and SEO to meet the minimum traffic requirements needed to qualify for an ad network.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Main Content Section: Affiliate Links -->
        <section id="tools" class="py-12">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-10 text-center">Your Zero-Cost Digital Toolkit (Affiliate Income Strategy)</h3>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

                <!-- Tool Card 1: Free Hosting & Builder -->
                <div class="affiliate-card bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl mr-4 text-orange-500">
                            <!-- Icon: Web Hosting SVG -->
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-8 h-8"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="15" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><polyline points="17 2 12 7 7 2"></polyline></svg>
                        </span>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Free Website Hosting (e.g., GitHub Pages)</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Host your static website, portfolio, or niche site entirely for free. Zero monthly fees means 100% profit when you start earning.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-red-500 mb-4">
                        Monetization Hook: Promoting a cheap domain registrar as an affiliate add-on.
                    </p>
                    <!-- UPDATED LINK WITH MOCK URL AND ONCLICK HANDLER -->
                    <a href="https://mock.hostingprovider.com/signup?aff_id=YOUR-HOST-ID" target="_blank" onclick="openAffiliateLink(event, 'Hosting Service');" class="affiliate-button block w-full text-center py-2 rounded-full text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-200 font-bold">
                        Get Started Free <span class="text-sm"> (Affiliate Link)</span>
                    </a>
                    <!-- END OF UPDATED LINK -->
                </div>

                <!-- Tool Card 2: Email Marketing -->
                <div class="affiliate-card bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl mr-4 text-purple-500">
                            <!-- Icon: Mail SVG -->
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-8 h-8"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg>
                        </span>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Free Email Marketing Service</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Build your audience and secure a powerful asset. Many services offer a forever-free plan up to 500 or 1,000 subscribers.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-red-500 mb-4">
                        Monetization Hook: Promoting the paid tier upgrade when the user's list grows past the free limit.
                    </p>
                    <!-- UPDATED LINK WITH MOCK URL AND ONCLICK HANDLER -->
                    <a href="https://mock.emailservice.com/free-plan?ref=YOUR-EMAIL-ID" target="_blank" onclick="openAffiliateLink(event, 'Email Service');" class="affiliate-button block w-full text-center py-2 rounded-full text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-200 font-bold">
                        Start Building Your List <span class="text-sm"> (Affiliate Link)</span>
                    </a>
                    <!-- END OF UPDATED LINK -->
                </div>

                <!-- Tool Card 3: Free Design Tool -->
                <div class="affiliate-card bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-400">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <span class="text-4xl mr-4 text-pink-500">
                            <!-- Icon: Pen Tool SVG -->
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-8 h-8"><path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"></path><path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l3-3z"></path><path d="M2 2l7.5 7.5"></path><path d="M4 11l4 4"></path><path d="M11 4l4 4"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Free Graphic Design Tool</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Create stunning social media graphics, blog images, and e-book covers without paying a designer or subscribing to expensive software.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-red-500 mb-4">
                        Monetization Hook: Promoting a premium stock photo site or paid version of the tool as an affiliate partner.
                    </p>
                    <!-- UPDATED LINK WITH MOCK URL AND ONCLICK HANDLER -->
                    <a href="https://mock.canva.com/register/free-version?partner=YOUR-DESIGN-ID" target="_blank" onclick="openAffiliateLink(event, 'Design Tool');" class="affiliate-button block w-full text-center py-2 rounded-full text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-200 font-bold">
                        Design Your Brand <span class="text-sm"> (Affiliate Link)</span>
                    </a>
                    <!-- END OF UPDATED LINK -->
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ad Revenue Mock Section -->
        <section id="income" class="py-12">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">Ad Revenue Placeholder</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">This section will be replaced with an automated display ad unit once the site qualifies for an ad network like Google AdSense. It generates passive income based on your traffic.</p>

            <!-- Mock Ad Unit (Designed to be eye-catching on mobile) -->
            <div class="bg-gray-200 border-4 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto shadow-inner h-36 flex items-center justify-center">
                <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700">
                    [ Placeholder for Google AdSense or Ezoic Display Ad - CPM/PPC Income ]
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Support/Donation Section (Zero-cost income stream) -->
        <section id="support" class="py-12 text-center bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mt-12 border-4 border-blue-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Like This Free Resource? Support Our Mission.</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-blue-700 mb-6">
                If you find our zero-cost guides helpful, consider supporting our work! Accepting donations via platforms like "Buy Me a Coffee" is a completely free, direct income stream for creators.
            </p>
            <!-- UPDATED DONATION LINK -->
            <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/yourincomehub" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-full shadow-lg text-white bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-600 transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                <span class="mr-2">☕</span> Buy Us a Coffee (Donation)
            </a>
            <!-- END OF UPDATED DONATION LINK -->
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- Success Message Modal (Simulates affiliate click tracking/disclosure) -->
    <div id="success-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-600 bg-opacity-75 flex items-center justify-center z-50 transition-opacity duration-300">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl max-w-sm w-11/12 transform transition-all duration-300 scale-100">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-3 flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2l4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                Affiliate Disclosure
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                <span id="modal-content">You are heading to an external link. If you purchase or upgrade, we receive a small commission.</span>
            </p>
            <button onclick="closeModal('success-modal');" class="w-full py-2 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-green-600 transition duration-200">
                Acknowledge & Close
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer with Mandatory Affiliate Disclosure -->
    <footer id="about" class="bg-gray-800 text-white mt-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 text-sm">
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <p class="mb-2">&copy; 2024 Zero-Cost Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">Affiliate Disclosure (Mandatory):</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400">This site earns income primarily through affiliate marketing and advertisements. When you click on links and make a purchase, we may receive a commission at no extra cost to you. This is how we keep the resources free.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Function to handle affiliate clicks: opens the link and shows the disclosure modal
        function openAffiliateLink(event, toolName) {
            event.preventDefault(); // Stop the default link action immediately
            const url = event.currentTarget.href;

            // 1. Show the modal with contextual disclosure
            document.getElementById('modal-content').innerHTML = `You are heading to a recommended tool: <strong>${toolName}</strong>. If you make a purchase, we earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. Thank you for your support!`;
            document.getElementById('success-modal').classList.remove('hidden');

            // 2. Open the link immediately in a new tab/window for optimal tracking
            window.open(url, '_blank');
        }

        // Function to close any modal
        function closeModal(modalId) {
            document.getElementById(modalId).classList.add('hidden');
        }

        // Simple script for smooth scrolling for internal links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
                    behavior: 'smooth'
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
